Deltona.WOCL: WOCL (105.9 FM) is a Classic Hits formatted broadcast radio station in Orlando, Florida, owned by Entercom. The station airs a classic hits format, focusing on music from 1970 (with a few songs per day from the 1960s) to 1989 with the core being the late 1970s and 1980s with even some 1990s. It is similar to the format used by sister station WCBS-FM in New York.
